{"word":"καθάπερ","slug":"καθάπερ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαϑάπερ</el></b> [= <el>ϰαϑ</el>’ <el>ἅπερ</el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ conj.\">conj.</a> or <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on parallel aspect <b>as, just as, even as <a href='B:520 3:4'>Ro 3:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:520 4:6'>4:6</a>; <a href='B:520 12:4'>12:4</a>; <a href='B:530 10:10'>1 Cor 10:10</a>; <a href='B:530 12:12'>12:12</a>; <a href='B:540 3:13'>2 Cor 3:13</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καθάπερ\">καθάπερ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπὸ\">ἀπὸ</a> ϰυρίου πνεύματος</el> as one might expect from the Lord’s spirit or in accordance with the L’<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sp.\">sp.</a> <b><a href='B:540 3:18'>2 Cor 3:18</a>.</b> W. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καί\">καί</a></el> (even) as also <b><a href='B:520 4:6'>Ro 4:6</a>; <a href='B:590 3:6'>1 Th 3:6</a>, <a href='B:590 3:12'>12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καθαίρω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καθάπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}